{
  "text": "In addition to studying vibration mechanism in main drive system with the consideration of nonlinearity, the control strategy is also a key point in vibration suppression. With the higher demand on speed and accuracy in modern cold rolling process, the traditional control method, such as PID, has not been qualified to manage those vibration pheromones, and some advanced control algorithms [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] are not suitable to deal with the problem of model nonlinearity in rolling process. Thus, a nonlinear control algorithm is necessary to deal with this situation.",
